Package com.bumptech.glide.load.model.file_descriptor

Interface Summary
FileDescriptorModelLoader<T> A base class for ModelLoaders that translate models into Files.
 

Class Summary
FileDescriptorFileLoader A ModelLoader For translating File models into ParcelFileDescriptor data.
FileDescriptorFileLoader.Factory The default ModelLoaderFactory for FileDescriptorFileLoaders.
FileDescriptorResourceLoader A ModelLoader For translating android resource id models into ParcelFileDescriptor data.
FileDescriptorResourceLoader.Factory The default factory for FileDescriptorResourceLoaders.
FileDescriptorStringLoader A ModelLoader For translating String models, such as file paths, into ParcelFileDescriptor data.
FileDescriptorStringLoader.Factory The default factory for FileDescriptorStringLoaders.
FileDescriptorUriLoader A ModelLoader For translating Uri models for local uris into ParcelFileDescriptor data.
FileDescriptorUriLoader.Factory The default factory for FileDescriptorUriLoaders.
